    <title>Refugees contributor: Amelia Kuch</title>
    <description>Amelia Kuch is a cross-disciplinary doctoral researcher working on topics of migration, land rights and water infrastructure. Based at the University of Edinburgh, she is currently completing a PhD thesis on the processes of naturalization of Burundian refugees in Tanzania.
